        Creating your notes is easy! Just follow these steps:\n
        \n
        1) Create a pdf document with your notes. Your notes must be in the format:\n
          <i>term</i>:<i>definition</i>;\n
             (For example: Learn:To gain or acquire knowledge;)\n
        \n
        2) The name of your pdf document will be used as the name of your course.\n
        \n
        2) Load the pdf document onto your phone.\n
        \n
        3) Press the "Get PDF" button.\n
        \n
        4) Locate and select your pdf file.\n
        \n
        5) Your notes have been loaded into the app! You can now play the games and learn in a more fun way!
